episodes.title: REACT!!! video I am in Twin Flames Universe Cult (present me watching past me) help I am in a cult!
episodes.description:
As you watch the old footage from when I was in Twin Flames Universe, notice how I spoke in terms of "twin flames," "divine union," and "ascension." These phrases were part of the cult's language, which aimed to control and manipulate members' beliefs and actions. It's alarming to see how deeply I was influenced by such deceptive rhetoric, and it's crucial to raise awareness about the tactics used by such groups.
